<!--
    MDM Event Settings Dialog
    MessageDialog subclass — global event settings + per-event on/off + fill type editor access.
    Controller: MDMEventSettingsDialog (src/gui/MDMEventSettingsDialog.lua)

    Layout (Y-down from fs25_dialogContentContainer top):
      Title / Global section (enabled toggle + frequency) / Per-event rows (10 rows)

    Per-event columns: Name | Enabled/Disabled toggle | Custom fills count | Edit | Force/Stop
    All buttons use 3-layer pattern: Bitmap bg + Button hit + Text label.

    Column positions (700px content area):
      Name      0px   250px
      Toggle  258px   115px
      Count   380px    75px
      Edit    462px    90px
      Force   558px   135px  (total span = 693px)
-->
